   :checkable-without-lean true
   :my-assessment "ACCEPTED ON THE ARGUMENT. e extracts the ego, so the effect surviving extraction must be the ego's alone; a product over the whole context is not that. This needs no proof assistant and I evaluated it unassisted. The refutation stands on its own."
   :status :accepted-argument-unverified-proof}

  {:id :ego-lambda-lawful
   :statement "`egoLambda` — transport the whole value context, emit only the annotation at ego, lambda(x) = ((x 1).1, fun s => (x s).2) — satisfies all four mixed axioms."
